The commission of inquiry into state capture will continue to hear Eskom related evidence from Nick Linnell. The Zondo Commission will also hear evidence from Eskom Group Executive, Dan Morakane, and the former Director Tsholofelo Molefe. JOHANNESBURG - Eskom will continue to top the agenda when the Zondo Commission resumes on Tuesday morning. Former Eskom consultant Nick Linnell was giving evidence on Monday when the commission had to adjourn early. This was due to a severe storm that hit parts of Gauteng. Former Eskom group executiveÂ  Dan Marokane and former director Tsholofelo Molefe are also expected to testify.